ygData.messageBody:
Very strange. Neither www.eqsongs.com nor eqsongs.com work for me.

I must be getting some type of response from Rokken's server since I can do
traceroutes to it, but must not be accepting ICMP packets. Well I'll just
chalk it up to some internet routing fluke and wait for a bit.

---Windleaf
